tool_description: human/api is a platform that makes human health data available through a RESTful web service. We make it very easy to securely get a human's current or past health data.
name: Human
title: Human

api_list.name: Blood glucose by date
api_list.description: Returns blood glucose readings for a specific date

api_list.name: Recent sleep
api_list.description: Returns a summary of the most recent sleep recordings
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://human.p.rapidapi.com/human/sleep"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "human.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
